\">https://lih.kg/1456156</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1455040\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1455040</a><br />\n歷史會記住你地。<br />\n岀埋d假熄燈圖，同散水撚文宣<br />\n本身大把人收工入去，依家真係多謝你地"},{"pid":"3f79fcbb23f20a3d2081ac301ad4a74f3e080a55","tid":1456670,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:02:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1CzmDQc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1CzmDQc.jpg&h=9a010b62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2105 接機"},{"pid":"1976a1042ae537dcd5f95d835e448cdc96e259c4","tid":1456670,"uid":282149,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:06:00.000Z","msg":"問題係你而家留喺度有咩用，已經停晒所有航班啦，如果等啲旅客走晒，你地先走嘅時候，俾人包抄就乜都冇，咁而家策略性走咗先，聽日再嚟過有咩問題？定係你哋想對住空氣宣傳五大訴求啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e75f479dc25779843b42dec9fbc3a00c5a7c542","tid":1456670,"uid":80592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:06:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">全世界食完飯返入機場<br />\n<br />\n文宣戰好撚重要<br />\n所有行動都需要宣傳<br />\n要反制國家宣傳機器<br />\n要話俾世界知我哋咁做嘅原因<br />\n喺文宣 網絡世界都要 Be humble<br />\n做事手法好重要<br />\n811同721嘅事一定要俾全世界知<br />\n<br />\n記者日日問721 811<br />\n831 五大訴求真普選百萬大遊行<br />\n要撐到9月搞大罷課<br />\n</div></strong></span><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">雖然抗爭時間久了，但絕對不能忘記，\n我們一直以來的理念，一定要堅持下去。</code></pre><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">繼續大力做藍絲文宣<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做事手法好重要<br />\n要壓制國家宣傳機器 文宣要大大力做<br />\n對內：AirDrop同路人 行動 戰略 方向<br />\n對外：Facebook 假acc扮中立拉攏藍絲<br />\nWhatsApp放分化藍絲嘅圖<br />\n地鐵站貼文宣 播片<br />\n國際：機場派外文文宣 播英文片<br />\n最新可以派埋文宣USB<br />\nQR Code 無用 無人會scan<br />\n</div></strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DrLgUUu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDrLgUUu.png&h=6550a2e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/28K11o3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F28K11o3.png&h=985d7652&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">冷靜思考 謀求對策</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">對準政權 勿生雜念</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">光復香港 時代革命</span><br />\n</div></strong>"},{"pid":"275549f0414566fc119dc76671c0d2871ea98fc4","tid":1456670,"uid":272028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c930d254eb3e7764cb79391808940dc6ea6a4164","tid":1456670,"uid":26106,"like":49,"dislike":3,"score":46,"quote":{"pid":"b8cc4a313876ee10477ab2f510f436e4463ed873","tid":1456670,"uid":186,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d0e9b2aeeb7fe69cdbacb0fef744ba322fc86d25","tid":1456670,"uid":186,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:38:15.000Z","msg":"進化到唔嘅片洗出兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:38:37.000Z","msg":"唔洗出兵*"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:40:56.000Z","msg":"咪on9啦<br />\n令機場癱瘓半日啦<br />\n想分化就收皮啦<br />\n你影張相代表到咩撚野？<br />\n我淨係知現場好多卧底狗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:06:24.000Z","msg":"以眼還眼 -&gt; 癱瘓機場 -&gt; 癱瘓半日機場<br />\n精神勝利黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1765362ed45667799da8f6783d278f648b53ed70","tid":1456670,"uid":119607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:07:16.000Z","msg":"2)所謂「三軍未動糧草先行」，想問一下留守ge人點樣解決運輸糧食同物資? 機場條路一封就係咁先，留守佔領意義何在。"},{"pid":"85b5786463357bc8e0a50871808eab6f50be3fba","tid":1456670,"uid":42246,"like":1,"disl